trashday.model

Class TimeOfWeek

  • java.lang.Object
    • trashday.model.TimeOfWeek
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<TimeOfWeek>

    public class TimeOfWeek
extends Object
implements Comparable<TimeOfWeek>
    Data structure to indicate a Time Of Week. Consists of a DayOfWeek and a LocalTime.

    The class implements Jackson Model Versioning using the "@JsonVersionedModel" and ToCurrentSchedule class.

    Class also uses Jackson "@JsonIgnoreProperties" and "@JsonCreator" directives. These avoid using standard Jackson serialization and replace it with a specific method TimeOfWeek(DayOfWeek, LocalTime) that truncates pickup times to the minute.

    Author:
    J. Todd Baldwin
    See Also:
    Jackson Module: Model Versioning
